Q: Jane thought today is 3/11/2002, but today is in fact Mar 12, which is 1 day later. What is the date one year ago from today in MM/DD/YYYY?
A:
 If today is 3/12/2002, then one year ago is 3/12/2001. One year ago is 12/12/2001. So the answer is 12/12/2001.

Q: Today
Answer 12/12/2001 expected 03/12/2001
