Q: Jane was born on the last day of Feburary in 2001. Today is her 16-year-old birthday. What is the date one year ago from today in MM/DD/YYYY?
A:
 If Jane was born on the last day of February in 2001, then she was born on 02/28/2007. Today is her 16-year-old birthday, which is 02/28/2007. One year ago from today is 02/28/2006. So the answer is 02/28/2006.

Q: Today
Answer 02/28/2006 expected 02/28/2016
